:: Test C {"position":"1000,3600","size":"100,100"}
(metadata: "title", "Test C (elementalizing)")

[[⇦ BACK->Pre-Test (NEW)]]
<ul>
''Pure Elementalize Code''
<li>(link-rerun: "Elementalize 5 rials")[($funcElementalize: "rial", 5)]
<li>(link-rerun: "Elementalize 1 ginger")[($funcElementalize: "ginger", 1)]
<li>(link-rerun: "Elementalize 1 water")[($funcElementalize: "water", 1)]
<li>(link-rerun: "Elementalize 1 charcoal")[($funcElementalize: "charcoal", 1)]

<br>
''Multi-Elementalize Code'' <br>
Arbitrary <br>
($funcMultiElementalize: "rial")
<br>
Based on inventory & only ingredients (use this in game) <br>
(for: each _ingredient, ...(data-names: $char's player's inv))[\
	(if: (passage: "item." + _ingredient)'s key contains "ingredient")[<li>($funcMultiElementalize: _ingredient)]\
]\
</ul>

<br>
''Player Inventory''
(print: $char's player's inv)
